00:24:22,961 --> 00:24:25,063
Maybe Mom remembered
her own blood type wrong.

552
00:24:25,130 --> 00:24:27,899
That's possible, from her personality.

553
00:24:29,334 --> 00:24:30,702
That's totally possible.

554
00:24:33,538 --> 00:24:34,739
ABECHAN STEWED BEEF OFFAL

555
00:24:49,888 --> 00:24:51,223
<i>Will you come to</i>

556
00:24:51,289 --> 00:24:53,258
<i>Sarashina Toyoda? I'm craving soba.</i>

557
00:24:56,528 --> 00:25:00,065
I'M GOING TO STAY HOME AND DRAW MANGA,
