563
00:25:46,711 --> 00:25:48,613
BLOOD TYPE O

564
00:25:49,681 --> 00:25:50,882
Type O…

565
00:25:52,183 --> 00:25:53,118
RISSEI GAKUIN UNIVERSITY

566
00:25:53,184 --> 00:25:55,720
Hey! I was just drunk!

567
00:25:55,787 --> 00:25:57,622
She was so drunk the other day.

568
00:25:57,689 --> 00:25:58,523
That's not true.

569
00:25:58,590 --> 00:26:00,125
Her eyes were like this.

570
00:26:00,692 --> 00:26:02,761
