572
00:26:03,795 --> 00:26:05,230
What is it?

573
00:26:05,297 --> 00:26:07,132
Look, he's already standing up.

574
00:26:07,198 --> 00:26:09,501
He's so enthusiastic to talk to her!

575
00:26:10,068 --> 00:26:11,002
She was Type O.

576
00:26:12,070 --> 00:26:13,438
Mom was Type O.

577
00:26:16,841 --> 00:26:17,676
I see.

578
00:26:18,643 --> 00:26:19,811
I'm going to test

579
00:26:19,878 --> 00:26:22,380
what my blood type is now.

580
00:26:22,447 --> 00:26:24,683
I'm going to go confirm that the Type AB

581
00:26:25,183 --> 00:26:27,085
that I tested from the blood drive

