to make me laugh.

589
00:26:51,676 --> 00:26:53,778
The position of my maternity handbook

590
00:26:53,845 --> 00:26:55,513
that I always put in here changed!

591
00:26:55,580 --> 00:26:57,782
It's always under the passport.

592
00:26:57,849 --> 00:26:59,584
And my drawer keys

593
00:26:59,651 --> 00:27:02,754
should be in this glass, but it was
in the glass next to it.

594
00:27:03,254 --> 00:27:04,923
Why do you just

595
00:27:04,990 --> 00:27:07,292
